node.text: What do you wish they had taught you in school? LMK in the comments down below. 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 13, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, child and people standing.

node.text:
CHILDHOOD: That’s me on the far right. I was 4. My brother Jordan on the left. My sister Joy in the middle. Looking at old photos like this fills my heart w so many emotions. Love. Nostalgia. Gratefulness. The day this photo was taken was probably a great day until I had to get on the bus and go to school 😂 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word "AIRBNB”. Thanks!
